    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "It makes the bus ride home feel like a dream. I’m walking back along the park and see that I’m going to get home before it finishes so take a moment to sit on a bench, smoke a cigarette and finish listening to what is the most amazing letter to a mother ever written. ",
            "link": null
          },
